<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Profile - BlogVerse</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #f4f5f7;
            --secondary-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-primary: #333333;
            --text-secondary: #666666;
            --accent-color: #4A90E2;
            --border-color: #E0E4E8;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .profile-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .profile-sidebar {
            background-color: var(--secondary-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            height: fit-content;
        }

        .profile-avatar {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .profile-username {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .profile-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-weight: 700;
            display: block;
        }

        .profile-main {
            background-color: var(--secondary-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .profile-tabs {
            display: flex;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .profile-tab {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .profile-tab:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
        }

        .profile-tab.active {
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .profile-content {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .blog-post {
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .blog-post-thumbnail {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .blog-post-details {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .blog-post-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .blog-post-meta {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .comment {
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .comment-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .comment-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .profile-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile-container">
        <!-- Profile Sidebar -->
        <div class="profile-sidebar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/150/150" alt="Profile Avatar" class="profile-avatar">
            <div class="profile-name">John Doe</div>
            <div class="profile-username">@johndoe</div>
            
            <div class="profile-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">42</span>
                    Blogs
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">256</span>
                    Followers
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">128</span>
                    Following
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile Main Content -->
        <div class="profile-main">
            <!-- Profile Tabs -->
            <div class="profile-tabs">
                <div class="profile-tab active" data-tab="blogs">Blogs</div>
                <div class="profile-tab" data-tab="comments">Comments</div>
                <div class="profile-tab" data-tab="about">About</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Profile Content -->
            <div class="profile-content">
                <!-- Blogs Tab -->
                <div class="tab-content" id="blogs" style="display: block;">
                    <div class="blog-post">
                        <img src="/api/placeholder/100/100" alt="Blog Thumbnail" class="blog-post-thumbnail">
                        <div class="blog-post-details">
                            <div class="blog-post-title">The Future of Blogging</div>
                            <div class="blog-post-meta">
                                Published on June 15, 2024 • 5 min read
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-post">
                        <img src="/api/placeholder/100/100" alt="Blog Thumbnail" class="blog-post-thumbnail">
                        <div class="blog-post-details">
                            <div class="blog-post-title">10 Tips for Content Creation</div>
                            <div class="blog-post-meta">
                                Published on May 22, 2024 • 7 min read
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Comments Tab -->
                <div class="tab-content" id="comments" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="comment">
                        <div class="comment-header">
                            <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" alt="Commenter Avatar" class="comment-avatar">
                            <strong>Jane Smith</strong> commented on <a href="#">The Future of Blogging</a>
                        </div>
                        <p>Great insights! I really appreciate the depth of analysis in this post.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="comment">
                        <div class="comment-header">
                            <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" alt="Commenter Avatar" class="comment-avatar">
                            <strong>Mike Johnson</strong> commented on <a href="#">10 Tips for Content Creation</a>
                        </div>
                        <p>These tips are extremely helpful for new content creators.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- About Tab -->
                <div class="tab-content" id="about" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>About Me</h3>
                    <p>Passionate writer and content creator with a love for technology, travel, and storytelling. Always eager to learn and share knowledge through blogging.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Contact Information</h4>
                    <p>Email: john.doe@example.com</p>
                    <p>Location: San Francisco, CA</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Tab switching functionality
        document.querySelectorAll('.profile-tab').forEach(tab => {
            tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
                // Remove active class from all tabs
                document.querySelectorAll('.profile-tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                
                // Add active class to clicked tab
                tab.classList.add('active');

                // Hide all tab contents
                document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(content => {
                    content.style.display = 'none';
                });

                // Show selected tab content
                document.getElementById(tab.dataset.tab).style.display = 'block';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>